WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.566 --> 00:00:03.433
Since Lady De entered the palace,

2
00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.266
the Empress Dowager’s health has started to deteriorate.

3
00:00:08.366 --> 00:00:10.500
I don’t know if it’s just a coincidence,

4
00:00:10.866 --> 00:00:13.166
but it’s true that after Lady De came to the palace,

5
00:00:13.333 --> 00:00:16.666
the Empress Dowager has become increasingly frail.

6
00:00:16.666 --> 00:00:18.500
But wasn’t the Empress Dowager’s illness

7
00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:20.766
caused by Lady Lin’s dark magic?

8
00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:21.666
At first,

9
00:00:21.666 --> 00:00:24.833
I also believed the illness was due to Lady Lin’s dark magic.

10
00:00:25.100 --> 00:00:26.566
After finding the child,

11
00:00:26.566 --> 00:00:28.600
the Empress Dowager did regain some clarity,

12
00:00:28.600 --> 00:00:30.766
but afterward, her condition

13
00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:32.833
deteriorated day by day.

14
00:00:33.500 --> 00:00:34.833
Even with the court physicians,

15
00:00:35.166 --> 00:00:36.766
there has been no improvement.

16
00:00:36.866 --> 00:00:40.066
In the previous life, the Empress Dowager was poisoned to death by Consort Guang.

17
00:00:40.333 --> 00:00:42.400
But now, she has been sent to the cold palace.

18
00:00:42.566 --> 00:00:45.300
Could she still have some extraordinary powers?

19
00:00:45.900 --> 00:00:47.200
Empress,

20
00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:51.600
now only you can save the Empress Dowager.

21
00:00:52.533 --> 00:00:53.700
Momo, don’t worry.

22
00:00:54.866 --> 00:00:56.600
Since I am aware of this matter,

23
00:00:56.600 --> 00:00:57.966
I will take responsibility.

24
00:00:58.133 --> 00:00:58.466
Momo,

25
00:00:58.466 --> 00:01:00.766
just continue taking good care of the Empress Dowager in the Cining Palace.

26
00:01:00.766 --> 00:01:02.333
Once I find out the truth,

27
00:01:02.333 --> 00:01:04.666
I will certainly inform you.

28
00:01:05.966 --> 00:01:08.666
Thank you, Empress.

29
00:01:14.366 --> 00:01:15.300
Then I will take my leave.

30
00:01:15.900 --> 00:01:17.500
I’ll take my leave now.

31
00:01:19.900 --> 00:01:20.700
Biyuan,

32
00:01:21.100 --> 00:01:21.900
Yes.

33
00:01:23.500 --> 00:01:24.466
You go.

34
00:01:27.400 --> 00:01:29.366
Empress, please have some tea.

35
00:01:29.900 --> 00:01:32.600
How did it go? Did you follow my instructions?

36
00:01:32.600 --> 00:01:34.200
Yes, I took a detour on my way back as you instructed.

37
00:01:34.200 --> 00:01:35.500
As you expected,

38
00:01:35.666 --> 00:01:37.300
the Yao Hua Palace is very lively.

39
00:01:39.400 --> 00:01:40.266
Oh,

40
00:01:40.266 --> 00:01:42.166
why is it so lively inside?

41
00:01:42.166 --> 00:01:43.300
Many of the ladies in the harem

42
00:01:43.300 --> 00:01:46.066
like to come here to have tea and chat with Lady De.

43
00:01:46.066 --> 00:01:49.533
Does Lady De treat you well?

44
00:01:49.533 --> 00:01:51.533
Lady De is very kind to her servants.

45
00:01:51.533 --> 00:01:53.600
She is very approachable.

46
00:01:53.600 --> 00:01:55.300
Which palace are you from?

47
00:01:55.300 --> 00:01:56.700
I’m from the Internal Affairs Bureau.

48
00:01:59.933 --> 00:02:02.066
It seems that your impression of her is correct.

49
00:02:02.733 --> 00:02:05.633
Could it be that Momo was overthinking it?
